220
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,000
Yes, Your Highness.

221
00:15:41,380 --> 00:15:42,780
[Lingxiang Pleasure House]

222
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:43,960
Miss, take a look.

223
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:46,000
