228
00:15:53,750 --> 00:15:54,480
Don't worry.

229
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,480
I'm fine.

230
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:57,720
The Di family and Jingnan

231
00:15:57,720 --> 00:15:59,240
