597
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:22,320
What are you doing here?

598
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,960
I came here after hearing from Jili
that you were here.

599
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:25,880
Your Highness.

600
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:31,880
Your Highness?

601
