716
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:39,360
I believe Ziyuan will be much happier.

717
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:43,230
This might be fate.

718
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:47,510
And that might be the best way
to use this flower.

